nd over.Eventually I just gave up on building the stupid ramp and on this game. Since this is a main mission, and you can't progress in the story until you complete it.Guess I'll just wait another year again.........Update 5/17/2017: (IT""S BETA again)The game is down to 5 official servers, 1 story and 4 adventure. Pointless to play on either. Story is progressed to far and adventure they have already a colony build (1 per server allowed) and you're not welcome.So my choices are.... play on a dead server, mess with port forwarding, or play a single player incomplete campaign game. Read that they're planning to make this a series of games. How about fixing this one first?My third mission I was to build a colony. WTF! Isn't colony building mid to late game???Also once you exit out of the game you must kill it in Task Manager, since it's still running in memory. That was a problem in EA, they fixed it, and now we're back to it again. Way to go!You'll also get missions that are incompletable. I've had to restart the game multiple times due to this. Or bad starting location, like an island with no land in sighjt.They've also removed the need to aquire scripts (blueprints) in Multiplayer. Now you automatically know everything with no option to turn this feature off. This is the worst idea yet.This also makes crafting difficult since the search option doesn't work most of the time, so you must scroll thru all the items trying to figure out in which category it's located.There are still placeholders for items that were never put in or items that have no function."
