romised a peaceful new start ... and so it begins [Aw Hell naw, I ain't gonna spoil it for you!]Npcs- Could use a wee bit of polishing, many of them are still as dumb as a rock ... but ah well, alpha wise some can talk and all can walk, that's fair.All in all, this is a brilliant game ... if you are looking for something to sink your teeth in, if you like games the allow you to desgin your own ways ... of travelling, fighting, living .... this is totally the game for you! However, mind you ... in order to thrive in this new world ... there are challenges to the mind ... if you think you got what it takes, then hop abroad the ship and off we go!See you soon, and safe space faring Colonists.- spongpol"
